The images are used on the site are
trademarks and copyrighted by our suppliers, only meant and authorized for
reselling their products. This Chinese site owner copied materials on our
site and resold their fake products. We have contacted them multiple times
to have the mentioned products taken down but they have not cooperated.
Furthermore, their positions in the search for many keywords were highly
promoted by Google regardless of their shady, shake practices.
